data.description: Welcome to Oconee County's Gated community Franklin Grove.  Located just off Hwy 78. This lovely home features a foyer entry, open concept living area with Kitchen, dining room and family room and fireplace perfect for entertaining.  Kitchen has solid surface countertops, 2 pantries for plenty of storage.  All 3 bedrooms up, large master bedroom and master bath features double vanities, separate tub and shower.  private alley garages, and sellers use the garage as additional outdoor space.  Community amenities include a swimming pool, club house, playground, exercise facility, tennis and pickleball courts.  This sought after location offers easy access to Hwy 78 and Hwy 316 and is located award winning  North Oconee High school district. You can be in downtown Athens in a few minutes or travel to quaint Historic Downtown Monroe for shopping and restaurants.  This beautiful home will NOT last long!
